The "output_and_shifter" block (RAM) operation is controlled by three most
significant bits ( I8, I7, I6) in the instruction. Thus there are eight 
possible cases.

The test vectors in "tv_op_sh.vhdl" test the "output_and_shifter" component in 
all modes of operation for each of the eight cases.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

(1)  Y gets F.

F <= "0101";             
A <= "1110";
Q <= "0000";           
I <= "000000000";
OEBAR <= '0';

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

(2)  Y gets tri-stated.

F <= "0101";            
A <= "0111";
Q <= "0000";            
I <= "000000000";
OEBAR <= '1';

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

(3)  Y gets F.

F <= "1110";            
A <= "0110";
Q <= "0000";           
I <= "001000000";
OEBAR <= '0';

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

(4)  Y gets A.

F <= "1110";             
A <= "0110";
Q <= "0000";           
I <= "010000000";
OEBAR <= '0';

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

(5)  Y gets F.

F <= "1110";             
A <= "0111";
Q <= "0000";           
I <= "011000000";
OEBAR <= '0';

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

(6)  Y gets F. RAM0 gets F(0). Q0 gets Q(0)

F <= "1001";             
A <= "1000";
Q <= "0100";           
I <= "100000000";
OEBAR <= '0';

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

(7)  Y gets F. RAM0 gets F(0). Q0 gets Q(0)

F <= "0110";             
A <= "1110";
Q <= "1101";    
I <= "101000000";
OEBAR <= '0';

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

(8) Y gets F. RAM3 gets F(3). Q3 gets Q(3)

F <= "0100";             
A <= "0010";
Q <= "1000";         
I <= "110000000";
OEBAR <= '0';

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

(9) Y gets F. RAM3 gets F(3). Q3 gets Q(3)

F <= "0001";             
A <= "1100";
Q <= "1000";        
I <= "111000000";
OEBAR <= '0';

-------------------------------------------------------------------------



